---
title: Cal Smart Double Shrimp and Zesty Slaw Tacos with Chipotle Sauce and Feta
description: Shrimp get a quick toss in the pan with our Enchilada Spice Blend in this easy and delicious weeknight dish. The lime-garlic slaw is refreshingly light, while the chipotle drizzle gives these handhelds a welcome kick.

